Package human

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HRFactory  
    HumanResource
    This abstract class is extended by all the human ressources of an ED : Th physician, the nurses, the patients and the transporters.
    Nurse
    Nurses are part of the human resources A nurse has a patient assigned when it is not idle : currentPatient
    Patient
    The patient is defined by different variables:
    name
    surname
    ID
    health insurance
    security level
    state (generated by default)
    location (null by default)
    history (empty arraylist by default)
    arrival time
    assigned physician (null by default)
    bill
    destination
    ED
    Physician
    Physicians are part of the human resources.
    Transporter
    Transporters are part of the human resources.
